1
00:00:01,294 --> 00:00:04,764
iz ven zent ir a- ongekumen in land arayn?

2
00:00:04,956 --> 00:00:10,991
un m'iz ongekumen in land arayn in far rosheshone.

3
00:00:11,065 --> 00:00:14,805
aroysgeforn zenen mir in tsvelftn LIPIEC. ze'mir gevezn

4
00:00:17,207 --> 00:00:22,820
vifl vifl vo- vifl? tsvelef teg in a tranzit lager in Bukhholts.

5
00:00:24,227 --> 00:00:29,570
un dem yor vos m'iz geven in in Bergn-Belzn hot men man gehandlt mit brilantn.

6
00:00:30,505 --> 00:00:34,923
un di rusishe misye hot dos oyfgekoyft, in Berlin iz gezesn a rusishe misye.

7
00:00:34,923 --> 00:00:40,609
dos iz gevezn biz peysekh. peysekh hot zikh di misye farmakht, hot er oyfgehert handlen.

8
00:00:40,609 --> 00:00:47,812
azoy, un in tsvishn tsayt iz gekumen a a briv fun mayn bruder az er ken mayn man nisht aribernemen

9
00:00:48,561 --> 00:00:50,951
keyn Kuba, nor mikh mitn kind.

10
00:00:51,430 --> 00:01:01,616
dervayl iz gevorn aktuel di tsen toyznt tsertifikatn, un fun der amerikaner zone flegn zey kumen batsoln finef t- tsen toyznt dolar far a sertifikat.

11
00:01:01,622 --> 00:01:04,147
far nemen tsu forn legal aher.

12
00:01:04,390 --> 00:01:13,946
un un mayn man iz gevezn a mitglid in linke politsye, hot er geshmirt mit finef toyznt dolar far undz ale dray, farn kind, far mir un far im.

13
00:01:13,946 --> 00:01:19,875
un biz der tsveyter TUR iz gekumen do aher, ze'mir tsvelef tog geven in tranzit lager,

14
00:01:20,607 --> 00:01:27,432
un iz geforn epes oyf a balye vos iz shoyn geforn dos dos letste mol,

15
00:01:27,432 --> 00:01:32,164
un m'iz ongekumen in land arayn iz shoyn geven, oyf der shif, oyf dem shifl,

16
00:01:32,164 --> 00:01:37,813
iz shoyn gevezn, biz s'iz aroyfgekumen fun Sokhnut epes fregn, iz shoyn geven shpet bay nakht,

17
00:01:38,072 --> 00:01:44,799
eynse, tsveleve, ver veyst, alnfals, un m'hot undz oyfgenumen undz o,

18
00:01:45,379 --> 00:01:51,785
m'hot gornisht farlangt, m'hot gornisht gevust, nor er hot proponirt az m'zol geyn in a KIBBUTZ arayn, BECHEN s'do a kind.

19
00:01:51,792 --> 00:01:54,716
mayn man hot fun dem nisht gevolt hern, er iz nisht geven keyn tip.

20
00:01:54,716 --> 00:01:58,282
bemeyle vos er hot getun hob ikh gemuzt tun, s'geven mayn man.

21
00:01:59,419 --> 00:02:06,534
ze'mir ongekumen keyn Givat Olga, iz nisht geven afile keyn balatake, shoyn tsveye bay nakht,

22
00:02:07,097 --> 00:02:13,368
ho'mir zikh gezetst, nisht genumen keyn betl, nisht keyn kots, nisht keyn akht lires, nisht gornisht,

23
00:02:13,577 --> 00:02:17,911
un in lager in tranzit, ikh m- mish UNK eyns in andern,

24
00:02:17,911 --> 00:02:21,064
hot men undz oysgeshit alts un tsugenumen a farmegn.

25
00:02:21,475 --> 00:02:23,646
un ikh hob nisht gehat far vemen optsushraybn.

26
00:02:23,787 --> 00:02:26,650
ober yetst tsurik dos, keyn Givat Olga.

27
00:02:26,082 --> 00:02:32,306
velkhe datum zent ir ongekumen in land? nayntsn, velkhes yor?

28
00:02:28,478 --> 00:02:31,189
far rosheshone ikh gedenk nisht genoy ven.

29
00:02:32,258 --> 00:02:35,610
iz iz iz zibn un fertsik.

30
00:02:32,306 --> 00:02:37,348
nayntsn zibn un fertsik.

31
00:02:36,797 --> 00:02:41,280
nayntsn zibn un fertsik far rosheshone, iz ven, oygust? oygust?

32
00:02:39,177 --> 00:02:41,223
september, oygust.

33
00:02:41,303 --> 00:02:46,927
un un m'iz ongekumen a a a dray vokhn far rosheshone.

34
00:02:46,927 --> 00:02:50,983
ikh gedenk nisht genoy dem termin, di minut gedenk ikh, azoy gedenk ikh yo.

35
00:02:48,255 --> 00:02:52,648
OK. oygust nayntsn zibn un fertsik.

36
00:02:51,411 --> 00:02:52,614
fertsik.

37
00:02:52,614 --> 00:02:58,865
alzo, mir hobn afilek nisht arayn in keyn balatke, m'hot nisht gebetn gornisht, s'nisht geven keyn keyn keyn az ma-

38
00:02:58,883 --> 00:03:03,674
az dakht zikh dos kind iz oykh gezesn mit undz unter a boym, biz s'iz lekhtik gevorn,

39
00:03:03,768 --> 00:03:08,999
ze'mir ho'mir genumen ze'mir arayn in shtot arayn, arayn oyfn KVISH,

40
00:03:08,999 --> 00:03:14,314
m'hot genumen a oyto, m'iz arayn keyn Tel-Aviv. vayl in Tel-Aviv oyf Binyamin zeks

41
00:03:14,314 --> 00:03:20,314
iz gevezn mayn shvogerl, a yingerer bruder fun mayn man, gekumen do mit Ander's armey.

42
00:03:20,374 --> 00:03:27,343
un dos iz geven a mishpokhe vu er iz gevezn oykhet, vu er iz ayngeshtanen, un er hot dortn take mit a tokhter khasene gehat.

43
00:03:27,343 --> 00:03:31,787
er lebt shoyn nisht un zi lebt shoyn oykh nisht. yingerer bruder fun mayn man.

44
00:03:34,122 --> 00:03:40,022
f- iz mit Ander's armey iz er do arayngekumen, azoy az er iz geven mit mit in kontakt,

45
00:03:40,838 --> 00:03:43,264
er hot gekro- er hot gevust az ikh leb,

46
00:03:43,264 --> 00:03:52,537
un fun vanet hot er gevust az ikh leb? vayl a sh- der shvoger, der advokat, iz gekumen hot iz geven in kontakt mit dem mit dem bruder vos ikh hob do gehat,

47
00:03:52,537 --> 00:03:58,296
un er hot azoy nokher dervust zikh az ikh leb mitn kind kind, nor der t- un zayn bruder nisht.

48
00:03:58,370 --> 00:04:04,703
azoy nokher hob i- mir gehat dem adres fun Nakhlat Binyamin zeks, dort iz geven der fotografist Progres,

49
00:04:04,716 --> 00:04:09,080
un zey zenen geven in der heykh, oyfn ershtn shtok hobn zey gehat,

50
00:04:09,103 --> 00:04:15,999
in in Varshe oykh gehat a fabrikn fun fotoraln. fotoraln heyst oyf fidlen di di dose.

51
00:04:16,225 --> 00:04:19,560
hobn zey do oykh gearbet, der zun,

52
00:04:19,752 --> 00:04:24,796
hot do oykhet gearbet, ober di eltern hobn gevoynt in Varshe, zenen gekumen fun Varshe.

53
00:04:24,844 --> 00:04:28,381
er iz do ahergekumen in land tsu nisht geyn in militer.

54
00:04:28,662 --> 00:04:33,566
iz mayn shvoger iz un ongekumen mit Ander's armey, iz er farforn tsu im,

55
00:04:33,657 --> 00:04:40,834
un m'iz geven bay im, iz gevezn etlekhene tekhter, di tsveyte tokhter hot er genumen far a froy, un beyde lebn nisht.

56
00:04:40,834 --> 00:04:42,732
ober es lebn tsvey kinder.

57
00:04:42,732 --> 00:04:51,237
di nemen fun fun mayn shver, dos heyst fun mayn man's tatn, un mayn mayn

58
00:04:51,237 --> 00:05:02,152
un di andere, neyn, di un a tokhter oykhet, heyst zi nisht nokh nokh der mame. nokh der mame heyst mayn tokhterl Sara. mayn man's.

59
00:05:03,559 --> 00:05:08,126
dos iz geven dos kumen aher. un dos iz geven m'hot zi mer nisht ongekukt,

60
00:05:08,571 --> 00:05:13,841
m'iz gekum- m'iz farforn tsu zey, ze'mir geshlofn bay dem shvoger, oyf, nokh nenter tsu tsu

61
00:05:13,841 --> 00:05:16,777
oyf a oyf a gas Zrubavel, nokh mer vi Zrubavel,

62
00:05:16,777 --> 00:05:22,065
far nokh Zrubavel nokh. nenter tsum tsum tsum metshet vos shteyt.

63
00:05:22,510 --> 00:05:25,339
ze'mir geshlofn, m'hot ongehoybn zukhn a dire.

64
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:32,696
geven ze'mir mitglider in der linker politsye in Bergn-Belzn, hot er gegebn finef toyznt dolar,

65
00:05:33,462 --> 00:05:36,521
Shmetenet, Smetana hot er geheysn.

66
00:05:36,521 --> 00:05:41,640
er iz dafke nisht er iz nisht gekumen keyn Yisroel, nor ergets farforn keyn Zid-Amerike.

67
00:05:41,848 --> 00:05:47,555
un ikh ikh hob mikh gevondn oyf keygn iber

68
00:05:47,666 --> 00:05:53,555
in in Histadrut ts- binyen oyf Brener iz gevezn di linke politsye.

69
00:05:53,555 --> 00:05:56,037
ikh bin aroyfgekumen, ikh hob getrofn epes a hoykerl,

70
00:05:56,037 --> 00:06:00,814
ikh hob mikh for- ikh hob nokh a legitimatsye, az m'iz geven mitglider in Bergn-Belzn.

71
00:06:00,814 --> 00:06:04,592
zogt er, iz ruf ikh mikh on, zog ikh

72
00:06:04,592 --> 00:06:10,185
ikh hob gehert az, SHIKUNIM hob ikh nisht gekent zogn, ikh hob nisht gevust in gantsn keyn UNK.

73
00:06:10,185 --> 00:06:16,148
vi azoy zog ikh, iz ho'mir ho'mir nisht keyn dire, un az m'hot m'hot gornisht genumen barn Sokhnut oykh gornisht.

74
00:06:16,148 --> 00:06:18,111
m'veyst nisht vu iz der Sokhnut.

75
00:06:18,111 --> 00:06:29,340
zogt er, undz boyen mir, ober vos, zogt er, s'hot a, vos iz der vider fun vanet du kumst yetst geyn darfstu bald hobn a BAYIT MESHUTAF hot er gerufn. zey hobn geboyt oyf Aleksander Yanay.

76
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:33,955
sheyne tsvey tsvey anderthalbn tsimern, heyst tsvey tsimern.

77
00:06:33,955 --> 00:06:36,216
a sheyne voynung, ikh bin dernokh gekumen in ir.

78
00:06:36,216 --> 00:06:39,743
zogt er, ir zent naye OLIM, darf men zen fun vanet tsu fardinen.

79
00:06:39,743 --> 00:06:43,976
s'take nisht ge- mayn man hot take nisht gekent fardinen keyn keyn lire tsen.

80
00:06:44,168 --> 00:06:51,367
s'iz take geven zeyer shver. alzo vos m'hot gehat, di brilantn gedekt oyf Kuba tsu forn, iz gevorn farkoyft,

81
00:06:51,694 --> 00:06:55,080
ikh hob arayngeleygt alts in der dire, zekhtsik shtign,

82
00:06:55,558 --> 00:07:04,142
punkt keygn iber dem metshet, di ershte koyln, eyder s'nokh geven a melukhe, eyder s'geven a regirung, hob ikh gehat in shtub, zekhtsik shtign heykh,

83
00:07:04,553 --> 00:07:12,081
un dernokhn in a tsayt m'hot oysgegebn dos gelt un aroysnemen punkt in tog fun tsvelef yor dortn voynen,

84
00:07:12,081 --> 00:07:20,156
hot men fun UNK tsen toyznt dolar, toyznt shekl opgekrign dray hundert. tsu di dire tsu.

85
00:07:23,571 --> 00:07:26,940
nu dos iz dos, ets vilt mit dem farendikn?

86
00:07:25,798 --> 00:07:31,158
di tokhter iz geblibn do in Erets Yisroel, zi hot onge- zi hot a mishpokhe?

87
00:07:29,162 --> 00:07:31,170
yo, yo.

88
00:07:31,170 --> 00:07:36,065
ober, yo, ober vos un ven, ir ir muzt mir, az nisht vel ikh nisht untershraybn gornisht.

89
00:07:34,725 --> 00:07:38,279
neyn, di tokhter vil nisht m'zol redn fun ir.

90
00:07:36,712 --> 00:07:41,302
n- neyn, ikh, ober ikh vel nisht untershraybn oyb ets vet mir nisht oysmekn dos.

91
00:07:38,837 --> 00:07:42,868
OK, nisht keyn problem. neyn neyn, m'vet ales oys-

92
00:07:41,543 --> 00:07:47,612
zi vil nisht hern. ikh hob opgenu- z- zi iz oysergeveyntlekhe tip.

93
00:07:48,715 --> 00:07:52,344
azoy vi, i- ikh ken azelkhe vos zenen geven in Rusland,

94
00:07:52,366 --> 00:07:56,579
un z- di eltern hobn nisht vos tsu dertseyln, un di kinder viln nor hern.

95
00:07:56,579 --> 00:08:01,770
zi vil keyn mol nisht hern. gornisht vil zi gedenken, un gornisht gedenkt zi.

96
00:08:01,860 --> 00:08:05,313
un zi vil nisht gedenken. un zi iz tsu mir shlekht.

97
00:08:05,164 --> 00:08:10,713
un ir klert a s- ir klert a sakh tsurik oyf di tsaytn, oyf di mishpokhe, oyf der milkhome?

98
00:08:10,956 --> 00:08:19,742
ikh hal- i- i- ikh ikh ikh makh ikh ikh hob tsu klern oyf nokh der milkhome. ikh hob mit dem man opgelebt akht un draysik un a halb yor.

99
00:08:19,090 --> 00:08:20,426
mit ayer man.

100
00:08:20,052 --> 00:08:24,459
yo, iz az s'kholemt zikh makho- iz er geven a zeyer a shverer eser.

101
00:08:24,459 --> 00:08:30,164
trots dem vos er iz geven a yosem fun der ershter velt milkhome, hot er lib gehat herlekh gegesn sheyn,

102
00:08:30,164 --> 00:08:33,640
vayl in di restoranen, er iz ge- m'iz geblibn a shtub mit yesoymim.

103
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:39,687
kholem red ikh nor vegn esn. oy, ikh hob gornisht in shtub.

104
00:08:40,099 --> 00:08:47,620
vayl bay mir kent ir take, far mir iz genug, nor ikh zol darfn oyfnemen mentshn azoy shtendik s'geven, hob ikh nisht.

105
00:08:48,098 --> 00:08:53,621
un der man shtendik mit esn ku- hot kumt er mir kapoyers, mit a gezelshaft mit farshidene zakhn.

106
00:08:53,621 --> 00:08:57,609
un ikh shlof nisht azoy shle- azoy fil ikh zol hobn ven tsu kholemen.

107
00:08:57,632 --> 00:09:01,544
az ikh z- ikh az az ikh her her ikh ikh nayes,

108
00:09:01,544 --> 00:09:06,675
gey ikh shlofn eynse, halb eyns, mit a NUMBER nokh azoy fil tabletn,

109
00:09:06,675 --> 00:09:12,134
haynt finef un ikh hob shoyn badorfn nemen dos tsveyte mol, hob ikh shoyn genumen tsvelef tabletn,

110
00:09:12,212 --> 00:09:19,850
eyder ikh nem di tabletn, eyb- i- eyder ikh derken, s'iz oys- s'iz oyssortirt, oyfn tish dortn zenen alts mayne retseptn.

111
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:24,171
s'iz do epes vos ir volt gevolt,

112
00:09:24,396 --> 00:09:31,072
un far vegn dem kind vegn, ir tort nisht, ir muzt mir tsuzogn ayer ern-vort er vet nisht dermanen zey.

113
00:09:24,430 --> 00:09:33,586
zog mir, neyn neyn, nisht vegn kind. nisht keyn problem, s'nisht keyn problem. BESEDER GAMUR.

114
00:09:31,112 --> 00:09:33,181
rayst oys di bletlekh.

115
00:09:33,593 --> 00:09:41,011
vayl ikh hob ir gegebn epes haynt a zog, ikh ken aykh nisht forshteln, ikh shem mikh tsu dertseyln vi vosere sof ikh hob gehat.

116
00:09:40,866 --> 00:09:44,761
OK, ir muzt nisht redn fun dos vos ir vilt nisht.

117
00:09:41,355 --> 00:09:43,391
ikh kokh in gantsn.

118
00:09:44,761 --> 00:09:56,959
ikh hob gevolt bloyz fregn, s'iz do epes vos ir volt gevolt zogn a far di yingere GE- generatsyon, far far mentshn vos hobn nisht mit gelebt dos vos ir hot mit gelebt.

119
00:09:50,113 --> 00:09:51,052
dos vil ikh.

120
00:09:55,378 --> 00:10:03,438
yo, koydem vil ikh zogn far di gelernte, far di profesorn. s'do a profesor Bauer, a u- a a a ungarisher.

121
00:10:03,664 --> 00:10:08,426
er hot nokh, zey hobn in gantsn di ungarn, er hot dokh zey gedekt, der keyser,

122
00:10:08,449 --> 00:10:14,236
zey hobn dokh fir, zenen dokh arayngeforn keyn Bergn-Belzn fir vokhn farn endikn di milkhome.

123
00:10:14,818 --> 00:10:22,996
zey hobn d- di rumener mer a bisl. di ungarisher hobn dokh in gantsn nisht ge- un hobn zikh gekent oysbahaltn, ikh ken a sakh.

124
00:10:23,661 --> 00:10:37,577
zogt er az er hot nokh gornisht gevust. a halbe milyon yidn iz hot gelebt in gantsn a sho. ikh hob aykh gevolt dertseyln, az dos gantse lebn keyn Treblinke hot gedoyert a sho. fun di transportn,

125
00:10:37,701 --> 00:10:40,648
m'hot zey nisht s'nisht s'bald geven a toytn-lager.

126
00:10:40,907 --> 00:10:52,427
yetst dos m'ruft on az s'iz geven tsum ersht, s'iz geven bald keyn shum ander zakh in Varsheve, bald a toytn lager.

127
00:10:53,614 --> 00:11:00,819
bald tsu shtarbn. un s'iz take ge- ale vegelekh mit alding. undz ho'mir gehat a shokhn voynen

128
00:11:00,846 --> 00:11:04,764
vos hot gearbet oyfn beys-almen, oyfn algemeynem fun Varshe.

129
00:11:04,764 --> 00:11:11,200
hot er gefirt, in di kantselarye iz er geven an ongeshtelter. a frumer mentsh nor a eleganter azoy fun di sheyn geputste.

130
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:13,300
hobn undz geha- un mayn man iz geven

131
00:11:13,325 --> 00:11:19,125
der vos hot tsunoyf genumen di dos gelter vi lang s'geven a por pyaster yede yedes mol

132
00:11:19,125 --> 00:11:23,625
oyf tsu kenen bagrobn, oder aroyshelfn azelkhe vos zenen shtar- geshtanen.

133
00:11:23,625 --> 00:11:26,375
azoy az m'hot gev- geven gut bakant.

134
00:11:26,375 --> 00:11:30,500
di mindst vos m'hot ongefirt in masn-kvorim,

135
00:11:30,500 --> 00:11:35,775
iz geven tsuzamen dos on registratsyes, zey hobn nisht gekent zdonzhen tsu makhn keyn registratsyes,

136
00:11:35,900 --> 00:11:42,795
tsvey hundert un zibetsik, tsvey hundert un akhtsik toyte, dray hundert toyte iz geven yedn tog. fun hunger.

137
00:11:42,795 --> 00:11:47,567
un koydem zenen geganen di vos zenen gevorn arayngeyogt oykhet. ober bald fun ershtn tog

138
00:11:47,567 --> 00:11:52,908
iz dokh gev- funem bombardirn fir fir vokhn zikh nisht untergebn iz dokh bald geven a hunger.

139
00:11:52,908 --> 00:11:57,158
meyle dos hobn di polyakn oykhet, ober zey hobn zikh ender an eytse gegebn.

140
00:11:57,158 --> 00:12:03,931
hobn zikh aroysgekrign oyf a provints, gebrengt fun fun di fun di derfer epes, ober yidn hobn dokh bald gelitn.

141
00:12:03,999 --> 00:12:06,112
nor nokh dem vi m'hot undz farmakht,

142
00:12:06,112 --> 00:12:14,044
un un nisht vayl, ven s'hot zikh geendikt di bombardi- di di di un zey hobn zikh er hot zikh untergegebn Stazhinski.

143
00:12:14,044 --> 00:12:20,249
iz bald geven toyt. nisht geven vi tsu fardinen, nisht gevezn keyner hot gornisht farmogt, alts iz geven bombardirt,

144
00:12:20,249 --> 00:12:24,716
zeltn s'geblibn a gantse shtub, dos iz bald geven a toytn lager.

145
00:12:26,832 --> 00:12:30,997
fun Kshevitski hot ir nokh gehert epes nokh dem?

146
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:35,297
o. bay Kshyevitskin hob ikh gezdonzhet, Varshe iz dokh geven in gantsn, yeder,

147
00:12:35,297 --> 00:12:39,135
dos der poylisher gegnt iz oykh geblibn nor a por hayzer vu di

148
00:12:39,135 --> 00:12:43,621
vu di di daytshn hobn zikh farhaltn biz der letster minut vi zey hobn opgetretn.

149
00:12:43,621 --> 00:12:47,162
oyf a oyf der gro- oyfn poylishn gegnt iz es gevezn.

150
00:12:47,162 --> 00:12:51,891
ikh bin dort geven take, s'geven der oysern MINISTERSTWO, ikh bin gegangen gevoyer vern vegn Kuba,

151
00:12:51,891 --> 00:12:54,000
ven s'mir geven akte- aktuel.

152
00:12:54,000 --> 00:13:01,081
bin ikh eyn mol adurkhgeyendik adurkh geganen oyf der dire vu er hot gevoynt,

153
00:13:01,780 --> 00:13:05,469
