zeyer raykhe mentshn gemuzt zayn. vayl in Varshe a a dire iz geven MASHEHU, nisht tsutsukumen.

158
00:13:29,590 --> 00:13:32,317
bin ikh aroyfgeganen, s'keyner nisht geven.

159
00:13:32,425 --> 00:13:40,176
eyns hob ikh gevust take fun Vroblevskin, az der bruder iz gefaln. in oyfshtand, ir bruder.

160
00:13:40,176 --> 00:13:46,503
un s'fun zey lebt ver s'geven a zun vos iz geganen in TICHON arayn, ge- zey hobn gelernt um- umlegal,

161
00:13:46,503 --> 00:13:49,782
di polyakn, s'hot dokh nisht getort zayn keyn shum shule nisht, gornisht.

162
00:13:50,312 --> 00:13:54,491
iz a zun mit a tokhter. un a mame zayne.

163
00:13:54,497 --> 00:13:57,528
keyner iz nisht geven, m'voynt nisht dortn.

164
00:13:57,552 --> 00:14:07,029
nor epes a a s'geshtanen aza, dos hot geheysn aza GABLOTKA hot es geheysn, mit shpiglen, a a a a shank,

165
00:14:07,525 --> 00:14:16,007
iz gelegn der kapelyush fun mayn man a hitl. fun di beste kapelyushn, mayn man's hitl.

166
00:14:16,182 --> 00:14:20,378
oysgeleydikte shtubn, ikh hob keynem nisht getrofn oyfn fertn shtok.

167
00:14:19,658 --> 00:14:22,284
ir hot zey keyn mol nisht tsurik getrofn?

168
00:14:21,244 --> 00:14:24,748
ikh ho- neyn. ikh hob nisht gevust tsi er lebt tsi nisht.

169
00:14:25,632 --> 00:14:29,861
dem Vroblevski vu dos kind iz geven iz tsurikgekumen fun Daytshland,

170
00:14:30,525 --> 00:14:32,679
bin ikh geven afilek mit mayn man

171
00:14:32,753 --> 00:14:36,392
un ikh hob im gevizn az vos der forheng, dos alts iz

172
00:14:36,668 --> 00:14:44,199
vos ikh hob gege- ober ikh hob im gezogt, ikh hob nisht gez- ikh hob nisht gezogt az er zol hern. er iz bay un- er hot im er hot mikh er hot bazukht oykhet.

173
00:14:44,199 --> 00:14:46,331
un m'iz geven in gute batsiungen.

174
00:14:48,615 --> 00:14:55,679
un bay dem Droshn bin ikh gevezn, hob ikh dertseylt aykh, der on dem fus, vos ikh hob dos kind oysgetsupt di nis.

175
00:14:50,910 --> 00:14:51,798
yo.

176
00:14:56,547 --> 00:15:05,968
un im Kshevyitskin hob ikh nisht ge- gehat ven, vayl ikh bin geven faryogt. ikh hob gearbet, un dernokh hot er mir ge- mayn man, der der man hot mikh gehitn,

177
00:15:05,968 --> 00:15:07,610
azoy vi an oyg in kop,

178
00:15:07,853 --> 00:15:13,686
ikh hob nokh im aroysgegebn dos esn vos der prezident hot gegesn hob ikh oykh gegesn, di zelbe kokh.

179
00:15:13,793 --> 00:15:20,782
m'hot mir gevashn dos zelbe azoy vi haynt, m'nemt fun far di far di fun fun fun far far di alte,

180
00:15:20,782 --> 00:15:26,161
di vesh, azoy hot men gegebn di zelbe vesheray hob ikh avekgege- vos vos Byerut,

181
00:15:27,124 --> 00:15:31,303
un ikh hob gehat a pensye vi er. dray hundert un fuftsik zlotes.

182
00:15:33,418 --> 00:15:40,314
a klal, az ikh ho- az ikh hob mikh nisht gekent optshepen, zog ikh, for UNK, heyb on handlen, bay dem man, er hot gornisht gevolt tun, er hot gevolt mikh hitn.

183
00:15:40,388 --> 00:15:48,802
heyb on oykh forn azoy vi ale. heyb on handlen. zogt er, ikh hob nisht mit vos ontsuheybn. hob ikh genumen tsvey pensyes foroys, zibn toyznt zlotes,

184
00:15:49,129 --> 00:15:53,325
far tsvey pensyes. iz er tsu morgns, ge- zogn mir di shikses,

185
00:15:53,466 --> 00:15:56,669
Ruta, UNK.

186
00:15:56,669 --> 00:15:59,839
dayn tseratene kapete shteyt shoyn in droysn.

187
00:16:00,368 --> 00:16:04,007
er iz gef- er hot er hot er iz nisht geforn in gantsn handlen.

188
