vos nokh vilt ir visn?

189
00:16:10,624 --> 00:16:15,820
dos muzt ir mikh, vu hot ir dose vos ir hot farshribn vegn mayn tokhter? ikh hob aykh oyfgegebn dem adres,

190
00:16:12,788 --> 00:16:15,600
yo yo, m'geyt es shoyn oysmekn,

191
00:16:15,820 --> 00:16:19,902
un ikh hob ay- ikh hob oyfgegebn di pletser vu zey arbetn. ir zolt visn,

192
00:16:17,985 --> 00:16:19,886
neyn neyn neyn, dos vet men,

193
00:16:19,902 --> 00:16:21,902
vifl ikh hob ongehakt di yorn,

194
00:16:21,902 --> 00:16:24,766
tsi ikh vel yo lebn, tsi ikh vel yo hobn an oyg, tsi,

195
00:16:24,766 --> 00:16:28,712
an oyg vel ikh shoyn nisht z-, keyn gants oyg nisht, ikh vel nor zen a bisele,

196
00:16:28,748 --> 00:16:34,798
vayl say vi un di, s'nishto keyn groyse hofenungen. ikh bin say vi nisht yung,

197
00:16:34,798 --> 00:16:38,381
un ikh bin k- s'nishto keyn krenk vos ikh hob nisht,

198
00:16:39,687 --> 00:16:44,321
dos ginokologish bin ikh dokh an akelt fun di daytshn.

199
00:16:44,563 --> 00:16:50,935
ikh bin dokh ikh bin gelegn, yo, in Bergn-Belzn bin ikh gelegn, in Bergn-Belzn bin ikh gelegn fir monat in shpitol.

200
00:16:46,622 --> 00:16:48,101
in Bergn-Bel-

201
00:16:52,090 --> 00:16:58,513
ayer dos yetst hot ir ir hot dertseylt dos vos ir hot iberlebt, un ayer tokhtern,

