00:16:58,536 --> 00:17:08,722
s'iz s'iz nisht vikhtik tsu di geshikhte iz iber hoypt nisht vikhtik. oyb ayer tokhter vil nisht m'zol redn fun ir muz men dos nisht tun, dos iz iber hoypt nisht,

203
00:17:06,990 --> 00:17:09,763
az nisht zolt visn,

204
00:17:09,218 --> 00:17:10,714
neyn neyn, s'iz sh-

205
