206
00:17:12,035 --> 00:17:18,306
nor dos vos zi muz mir helfn, zi muz mikh, zi muz mit mir geyn in shpitol arayn forn, nemt zi zikh CHOFESH

207
00:17:13,555 --> 00:17:17,936
