208
00:17:18,306 --> 00:17:19,333
ekstere.

209
00:17:19,333 --> 00:17:25,873
zolt ir visn ikh vel dos oy- mer keyn hilf zet ir nisht. ir kent azoy zen keyn lebedikn mentshn kumt nisht tsu mir.

210
00:17:21,807 --> 00:17:23,134
neyn neyn.

211
00:17:25,878 --> 00:17:27,262
